<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="immediately-conj">immediately <strong><em>conj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪ'miːdiətli/    美 /ɪ'miːdiətli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-as-soon-as">1.★ <strong>一...就... (as soon as)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I left immediately the clock struck 12.
12点的钟声一响我就离开了。</p></div></div>